creator: Windmill Air
descriptionHtml:
The Windmill Air is powerful, quiet, and eco-friendly. Use this app to:
1. Control your AC from anywhere. Turn it on 10 minutes before you get home or shut it off in case you forget!
2. Set schedules so your AC turns on and off automatically based on your lifestyle.
3. Adjust the Windmill Air settings with ease, helping you create the perfect home environment.
